{"tid":2367559,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原來Telegram老細Pavel Durov咁靚仔...","createTime":"2021-01-15T12:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T13:00:42.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d78f48cc5c44b90efabbcb0d5f5345ec05f205fb","tid":2367559,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:33:51.000Z","msg":"近日本港最大嘅新聞，相信就係通訊軟件大遷徙，全球Whatsapp用家已經不再信任呢個軟件，深信佢哋將自己嘅訊息傳給母公司Facebook，因此決定轉用Signal或Telegram。對於Telegram相信大家都唔陌生，呢個通訊軟件過去在兩年在香港使用率大增，但你又知唔知佢嘅創辦人係咩人?<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2021/1/14/2d2456271feb0098d7020f2122b72e4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2021%2F1%2F14%2F2d2456271feb0098d7020f2122b72e4f.jpg&h=5a0f1b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為科網巨頭，相信大家都對Facebook老闆朱克伯格好認識，36歲嘅佢資產已經超過1000億美元。而同樣36歲嘅杜羅夫Pavel Durov，你可能對呢個名無乜印象，但相信不久將來你都會認識佢，佢就係Telegram嘅創辦人，一名嚟自俄羅斯嘅戰鬥民族。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/durov/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdurov%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=3406ffaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/durov/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n2004年21歲嘅朱克伯格正式開徽啟Facebook傳奇，而當時正在讀大學嘅杜羅夫同樣擁有天才級別嘅程式及駭客技術，佢視朱克伯格為偶像，最終2006年大學畢業後成功創立同Facebook接近一樣嘅俄羅斯社群網站VKontakte。而VKontakte於俄國入面係非常成功的，並亦令杜羅夫擁有一切。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/durov/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdurov%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=3406ffaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/durov/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n不過好景不常，杜羅夫被俄國政府盯上，因為VKontakte上面有太多反政府訊息，因此普京明顯要出手打壓言論自由。最終，俄政府動用一切去將VKontakte國有化，而杜羅夫被迫出售自己所有股份，並秘密離開俄國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/durov/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdurov%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=3406ffaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/durov/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n離開俄國後，杜羅夫同佢嘅團隊東山再起，憑住賣掉VKontakte嘅錢開發出加密通訊軟件Telegram，隨後其用戶數量可以用爆發性嚟形容，甚至喺Facebook收購whatsapp後就更加誇張，如今已經成為全球最受歡迎嘅通訊軟件之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/durov/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdurov%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFuPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=3406ffaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/durov/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n而杜羅夫本人，自從離開俄國之後，就同佢嘅團隊每逢一段時間就去第二個地方居住，成為一班技術極尖嘅流放者，並一直做住改變世界嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n而同Facebook老闆朱克伯格唔同嘅係，杜羅夫真係靚仔得多！！"},{"pid":"f5ad42bb1a58f8990dd3d659a3be21e662e09d44","tid":2367559,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"鬼仔真係無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b4066cf9ee6f583454cd66e8fc61fa793d7464","tid":2367559,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"朱西保格係et<br />\nPavel係有外又有內在既絕世好男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b933f892cede1fa4f1bf8014c4ecbf616deb1895","tid":2367559,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"會唔會太型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebce2df9e884d481da46f35fed52b56d0231aecd","tid":2367559,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b933f892cede1fa4f1bf8014c4ecbf616deb1895","tid":2367559,"uid":22